Start
/ Plane — %x.size% (the content key) and %x!size% (the typed property) are distinct, no shadowing.
/ Sigil picks the plane: . = data, ! = property + envelope.
- set %x% = '{"size": 10, "name": "box"}', type=json
- set %x!size% = 28
- assert %x.size% equals 10
- assert %x!size% equals 28
- assert %x.name% equals "box"
